---
title: Easy Peasy Tofu Tetrazzini with Linguine
description: Italian-seasoned tofu takes centre stage and tops tonight's creamy masterpiece. This dish is filled with garlicky cream sauce, fresh tomatoes, spinach and caramelized onions...need we say more?
